## Component Standards

### Cards
- Always: bg-[#0f1522] border border-[#1f2d47] rounded-[14px]
- Stat cards: add top-edge glow inside:
  <div className="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#3b6ef5]/30 to-transparent" />

### Inputs
- Always: bg-[#141d2e] border border-[#1f2d47] rounded-[10px]
- Focus: focus:border-[#3b6ef5] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#3b6ef5]
- Placeholder: placeholder:text-[#4d5f7a]

### Buttons
- Primary: bg-[#3b6ef5] hover:bg-[#4d7ef6] rounded-[10px] font-semibold. Mobile: active:scale-[0.98]
- Secondary: border border-[#1f2d47] bg-[#0f1522] text-[#8494b4] rounded-[10px]; hover:border-[#3b6ef5] hover:text-[#3b6ef5]
- Sizes: default 11px 20px 14px; sm 7px 14px 13px rounded-[8px]; lg 15px 28px 15px rounded-[12px]
- Danger: bg-rose-500/10 text-rose-400 border-rose-500/25. Ghost: transparent, text-[#8494b4]

### Badges
- Shortlisted: border-[#3b6ef5]/25 bg-[#3b6ef5]/10 text-[#3b6ef5] rounded-[6px]
- Pending: border-[#1f2d47] bg-[#1a2438] text-[#8494b4] rounded-[6px]
- Rejected: border-rose-500/25 bg-rose-500/10 text-rose-400 rounded-[6px]

### Navigation
- Header: bg-[#090d16]/90 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-[#1f2d47]
- Active: text-[#3b6ef5] rounded-[8px]
- Inactive: text-[#8494b4] hover:text-white rounded-[8px]

### Tabs
- TabsList: bg-[#090d16] border border-[#1f2d47] rounded-[10px]
- TabsTrigger inactive: text-[#8494b4] rounded-[8px]
- TabsTrigger active: bg-[#3b6ef5] text-white rounded-[8px]

### Skeleton Loaders
- ALWAYS on async Supabase fetches — never blank state
- bg-[#0f1522] border border-[#1f2d47] rounded-[14px] overflow-hidden relative
- Shimmer: absolute inset-0 -translate-x-full animate-[shimmer_1.5s_infinite]
  bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/[0.04] to-transparent

### Match Score Ring (MatchScoreRing.tsx)
- SVG donut: r=16, strokeWidth=3.5, circumference=100.53
- Emerald ≥80, Amber 60-79, Rose <60
- Track: #1a2438

### Apply Drawer
- Vaul bottom sheet only — never centered modal
- bg-[#0f1522] border-t border-[#1f2d47] rounded-t-[20px]
- Handle: w-9 h-1 bg-[#243352] mx-auto (36px × 4px, rounded-full)

### Step wizard (candidate onboarding)
- Always show "Step X of 4". Progress is the emotional hook.
- Step circle: 28px, border-2 border-[#243352], done = bg-[#3b6ef5] text-white, active = ring 4px bg-[#3b6ef5]/12
- Connector line: 1px; done segment = bg-[#3b6ef5]

### Toasts / notifications
- bg-[#141d2e] border border-[#243352] rounded-[12px] padding, icon + title + subtitle
- Success: icon bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400. Info: bg-[#3b6ef5]/10 text-[#3b6ef5]

### Empty states
- Centred block: icon 52px rounded-[14px] bg-[#141d2e] border, title font-semibold, description text-[#8494b4], primary CTA button

### Design principles crib (from design system)
- Surfaces: bg #090d16, surface #0f1522, surface-2 #141d2e, border #1f2d47. No dot grids.
- Brand: blue #3b6ef5; Truth Engine = semantic only (emerald/amber/rose).
- DM Sans + DM Mono. Max 3 candidate fields, 5 recruiter. Skeleton on all async. Postcode outward only. RTW "(Self-declared)". Apply = Vaul bottom sheet. tabular-nums on all numeric. No Inter, no full postcode, no centred apply modal.

